result.adr_address: 126 Caine Rd, Mid-Levels, Hong Kong
result.name: Tsai Sing Restaurant

reviews.text: Good value for the money. Proprietors (husband & wife) are friendly.

Like a family restaurant, limited Chinese set, pasta set and steak set were available from lunch to dinner.  Late breakfast and afternoon tea set were also offered.  The taste was a bit salty to me.  However, the quality and quantity were acceptable in terms of price.  The place served neighborhood in general.
It's too tasty for me to take a photo before finishinh it.
Classic Hong Kong style tea house, reasonable price and good food.
I don't remember so it wasn't impressive
